â”‚   â”‚   â””â”€â”€ front/          # ğŸŒ Frontend layout
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ components/         # ğŸ§© Reusable components
â”œâ”€â”€ scss/                   # ğŸ¨ Styles (customize here)
